You will need MLton (http://www.mlton.org) installed in order to compile this project.  Running 'make' in the src/ directory should be sufficient to build the 'lml' binary.

Usage:

ml2pp0 file.sml

There are small examples in the doc/examples directory, with more coming soon, I hope.

